				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=2769&amp;sid=c541013560c3e5a31ba880f59f40f8ff#2769"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Wed Nov 27, 2002 1:44 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Experiences from a 52 mage on a Zek server</span></td>
				<td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=2769&amp;sid=c541013560c3e5a31ba880f59f40f8ff"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
